WEBVTT

00:08:29.330 --> 00:08:33.243
a lahko izberem roza ali modro pižamo.

00:08:33.243 --> 00:08:35.482
To ni participacija

00:08:35.482 --> 00:08:39.227
in vlade tehnologije ne uporabljajo dobro,

00:08:39.227 --> 00:08:42.130
da bi omogočile participacijo

00:08:42.130 --> 00:08:44.080
pri pomembnih temah:

00:08:44.080 --> 00:08:46.393
kako razporedimo proračun,

00:08:46.393 --> 00:08:48.615
kako izkoristimo prostor,

00:08:48.615 --> 00:08:52.164
kako upravljamo z naravnimi viri.

00:08:52.164 --> 00:08:54.278
To so odločitve,

00:08:54.278 --> 00:08:57.158
ki vplivajo na globalne probleme,

00:08:57.158 --> 00:09:00.980
ki se odražajo v mestih.